{"tid":1679911,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"3d printing +this person does not exist 可唔可以擊敗人面辨識？","createTime":"2019-10-28T12:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T11:37:28.000Z","uid":101662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"54ac764e7a8b45a3a77d82b564f7a555bf63d393","tid":1679911,"uid":101662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"我都知戴面巾戴帽遮面有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過如果一開始就show一個唔存在嘅人樣出嚟呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thispersondoesnotexist.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthispersondoesnotexist.com%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD545RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=687456fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://thispersondoesnotexist.com/</a> 會隨機gen一啲唔存在嘅人樣出嚟，如果用3d printing print出嚟再好貼服咁痴喺塊面到（未諗到點做），係咪可以喺完全唔引起人懷疑嘅情況下隨時勇武？<br />\n<br />\n仲唔會驚退場換衫比人跟/偷拍，直接引導相關部門拎住個錯嘅人樣去調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至唔洗好似家下咁喺公海吹雞用人手掩護，失驚無神幾條友突襲完狗屋就走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相關技術普及得到嘅話，face recognition形同虛設（除非啲狗7&times;24周街check身份證，或者你比人當場捉到）<br />\n<br />\n利申 純粹科技討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc617d819d368c26fc2cccad8b7565cb0cb4cda5","tid":1679911,"uid":175593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OY70OIS8bxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOY70OIS8bxs&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD545RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=2f422d71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OY70OIS8bxs</a><br />\n<br />\n依個有得搞,但係點mass production係問題"},{"pid":"0399870bd89fc2b559de93a1347ac8f55704cd22","tid":1679911,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc11fe8cb8bcb5538635e